Oluseun Anikulapo Kuti (commonly known as Seun Kuti) is a Nigerian musician, and the youngest son of legendary Afrobeat pioneer Fela Kuti. Seun leads his father's former band Egypt 80. Seun first played with Egypt 80 when he was only 8 years old.
